values:
even if i'm partying alone!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

Look, my birthday is friday and festivities will be taking place thursday night at club boca and friday night at the cove....  anyone and everyone is invited....  hit me up on my cell if you don't know where these places are or you need to come early and need a place to chill or you don't wanna have to drive home....  whatever....  i'm not sure what time thursday's popping off, but friday will start at 5:30ish at the cove (as long as one of my lovely co-workers will take the extra hour for me)....  call me on my cell and tell me if u wanna come....
all you have in this world is yourself....  don't fall into the delusion that you might have someone else....

I got "tagged" by Cat so here it goes:

my list of things of random things that I love to do no matter what that make me happy/lower my blood pressure/stress level...

~walks on the beach by myself
~a glass of white zin
~talking to friends
~getting to know people
~twisting 1 up
~dancing and singing when no one's home
~going for a walk
~being productive (as neurotic as that is)
~cuddling
~driving around in silence

I'm sure there are many other, but i'll have to think of them later....

this story is for everyone that might not believe that matt and i aren't really friends any more...

so i'm at chili's last night with stephanie, her sister, and these 2 guys.  i'm at the table, and it's getting close to closing, so not too many people were in the restarant.  I'm sitting on the side of the table at which i can see everyone going to and leaving the bathroom.  anyway, i see this guy leaving the bathroom and we make eye contact full on.  Now, I'm a little buzzed, but i realize it's matt so i smile and he looks at me like a deer in headlights....
then he bolts...
then i go outside to soak up what happened while steph's sister smoke a cig and low and behold, matt comes running out...  again, he can't even say hi and he and his girlfriend run to the car and then fly past me and sam sitting outside....

so, yeah.... we had been talking before all this, even yesterday when i told him that i was going to chili's with steph...  he knew i'd be there, couldn't say hi even when he saw me... so yeah, we're not even acquaintences...  if we were, he would've said hi...

whatever, 5 years down the drain...

have you ever had so much going on in your mind, but no one to talk to about it?

it's driving me nuts, so i'm gonna out with it here....
...  my life is a mess right now...
i know it's my mindset that's putting me there, but the two people i got used to venting to, the two people that used listen no matter what, are gone... one physically and the other mentally...
but the physical one is another subject of it's own (by the way, whenever you do read this, asuming you ever go on-line again, i just want u to know i'm thinking about u and praying for u every night and day)...

back to my story...
...  my life is just a waste of time and my time is just a waste of life...  i feel so dumb...
i invested all this time, all my heart, and everything i had and now i have realized it was all a waste...  my heart bleeds and i've been told to put my emotions on mute...  i'm used to having a rock by my side and now i'm alone and it hurts...  i know that this is all for the best and everything will be fine (i mean there are parts of this change that i look forward to, namely finding myself and not some vision of myself), but i'm afraid that i will never be able to invest my emotions in anything again...  repeatedly i've been hurt and it seems like now my brain realizes the sting...  the worst part is, is that i've gone back and just got hurt again, it's like i keep getting shocked and i refuse to let the shock keep me from what i want...  why am i so stupid, so stubborn?  

life to me, right now, just seems like a waste...  i mean, i used to think the point of life was to love and now i realize that loving just makes you weak...  now here i am, alone and scared...  i guess alone isn't the right word, i have friends, some really great ones, but it feels like a huge part of me is missing, broken, hurting...

i know, i sound like a stupid immature brat but i had to let this out... you didn't have to read it if you didn't want to...

so yeah, today's a shitty day....  i found out i might not have my scholarship for next year, but u know what, that has been on of the not-so-bad parts....  my little baby terra had to be out to sleep today.... i'm gonna miss her :(

R.I.P. Terra

Name:Jill Marie
Age: 22
Location: about 100 feet from fau boca
Year: junior/seniorish
Major/Minor: Business Management and Accounting

Name a few of your favorite...
Bands: i'm more into rap and hip/hop....  they don't really have bands....
Movies: any movie that takes you on an emotional rollercoaster or is great to watch with a bowl and some fire!
Books: i wish i had time to read for enjoyment!
Interests: acting, singing, dancing, MEN and men only (thanks to whoever got my password and changed that though!!!!!!!!!), goofing off and having fun!

I love Fau because i like to meet people....  i hate too many things to mention though!
danny bought me some wendy's....  thanks danny :)

i would have to say that this was my very fav. v-day ever....  it started on saturday with some arby's and planning a tattoo with matt...  then, sunday it continued with some more matt and him giving my my v-day gift...  then monday i woke up to texts from some people and a card and cd from my mom, and then at work i got delicious chocolates and a cd from danny and a bear from the vermont bear company from someone who won't admit to sending it to me, and then i had some dinner with 3, count them one-two-three hot stud-muffins (aka Steve, John, and Mike)... now, it was nothing like i had planned my v-day to be, but it was better than if my plans had worked out...
... now back to the real world....

life at ths point is ok....  i might even say i'm content with the happenings of now, just wsh i had more time, always wishing for more time...

school's hard and getting annoying, but i dropped a class today so things should be getting better...

work's good, but i'm not to sure of what's next.... i mean i love working at the pharmacy...  it's fun and i like the people there...  ok, the customer's suck, but that's gonna happen anywhere...  anyway, i know i'm gonna keep this job for a long time but i feel this timer going off in my mind telling me that i need to figure out what's next...  i need to know what i'm gonna be doing when i get out of school...  whatever, i'll shrug it off for a bit more...

my social life...  oh wait, i have no social life...  i mean, it's not like i care that much, but it seems as though i never have the money or time to do stuff...  well, i never have the money and the time i have is on the weekends, just i'm too tired on friday after getting out of work at 8 and saturday's when i get off work at 10 i'm WAY too tired to even think about getting ready to go out....  well, i'm not just tired, i'm sick right now and have been since the beginning of the year, but even that will be over with hopfully in a week or two (the worst of it is yet to come though)...

as for life, it's alright...  no major drama right now which is good... i seem to keep meeting guys which is nice, but i know it's not gonna lead anywhere...  it can't...  i don't have the time to even think about starting a relationship especially with the people that are in my life now... i barely have time for them and that's hard enough...  

anyway, just a little update...  i am happy right now, for no reason either....

the passion's there, but you're not...

you no longer take me where i need to go...
i'm done with being unfulfilled...
i tried my hardest to let you know...
but now i know i need to be thrilled ...

i told myself this year would be different...
i told myself i'm not gonna play games...
i told myself i have to stick to my limits...
now it's time to live up to my claims....

because it's you, you have another shot...
becuase it's you, and "in the now" i'm caught...
but because it's new me, your chance is not really fair...
but becuase it's old you, either way, you won't care...

so maybe i should decide now's the time to quit...
maybe i should give up you before i give a shit...
maybe i should stop this and just run...
maybe now before i'm your next big pun....

so steve gets a big thanks from me...  he gave the the absolutely most handy thing-a-ma-jig i think i have ever gotten...  it's a key-chain hanger thingy that has a flashlight attached to it...  this flash-light has been so handy sneaking in and out of my mom's house when i just wanna grab something without her even knowing i was there....  so steve, big props to you....

life as i know is changing and i'm doing it on purpose... i need to change, to evolve...  i'm done with being comfortable and ready to chance some comfort and lonely times to become a better person...  i need to grow...
so i've learned a few things about myself and it's just the beginning of my metamorphis...  i've learned that i'm not willing to settle just to not be lonely...  i've learned that i'm a lot stronger than i think and that i'm tons of fun by myself....  anyway, this is just the beginning, like i said...  we'll see how well it goes...

so i'm in my accounting class talking to my friend akeem and we start talking about the work we have to do...  next week we have 3 chapters due (which takes about 4 hours to complete the work for each chapter)...  THAT'S 12 HOURS OF WORK!!!!  normally, i'd just not do it, but my teacher is collecting it all...  not only that but we have to take 5 chapter tests online by friday of next week...  each test takes about 1 hour...  THAT'S 17 HOURS OF WORK FOR 1 FUCKING CLASS!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!  not only that but also i have a quiz next week in my cross culture class on tuesday on a chapter and a case that i have to look up... and i have to do free cash flow statements for 3 major companies (which i have to research the companies first and then do the statements) which will be collected in my finance clas on tuesday....  man, i have one more class today and i bet i'll have an assignment to be collected by him due for tuesday too!!!!  school is raping me in the ass and totally not using lube!!!!!!  i mean, i know i have no life already, but it's the 2nd week of class and i thought i'd have a little bit of time to myself this week!  so, if you don't see me until summer it's b/c i'm hiding in my dungeon doing school work!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!  I CAN'T WAIT TO GRADUATE!!!!!!!  i think i'm gonna get out earlier than planned...  i think i'm gonna take summer classes so i can stop this bull shit!
danny bought me a parting salad and is forcing me to write about it in my journal....

seeing as how my father is now engaged and living with his fiance in broward, his house is empty...  he decided to give me a key and tell me i can stay there...  so if anyone wants to stop-by, call me...

I hope everyone had a merry christmas!
mine was good...  lots of family shit and some fighting, but it was good in the sense that it made me realize some of my new years resolutions...

I hope everyone got what they wanted and whatnot...  i hope the night was spent with people you really care about...  i hope that your hearts were content when you closed your eyes and went to sleep...  my heart seemed to not be, but i'm sure that'll change soon enough...
 
You keep holding me down...
you keep tearing me apart...
i'm sad when you're not around...
but when you are, u rip out my heart...
you kill me with your kind words,
to set me up for the fall...
i'm done with living for u...
i'm done giving u my all...
this next year's gonna be different,
because now i'm pissed...
the next year's gonna be different,
because i can't live for this...
i don't need your "i-love-you's",
i won't need to know you're there...
i don't need you killing me inside...
i think now i've had my share...
i wish you didn't cause me so much pain...
but i think u might never stop...
i've had my share of this game...
i'll miss you, you are all i've got...

... my heart will become stone....

well, eventhough this weekend's plans got fucked up, the party must go on...  tonight i'm still gonna do something cool, even if it's avoid everything else like the plague...  i mean, i got my bag of tricks and dammit someone's gonna get a nice surprise this weekend!!!!!!!!

matt and i had a really interesting conversation yesterday...  of course, we were driving around so i can't remember most of it, but i do remember some...  it's funny how everyone says we gage our life on pain...  i believe that, but i think it's all because of what we were taught...  i don't think it's a universal human condition, i think it's the american way of life...  i truly believe that it can be reversed though...  one way is for people to live the four agreements...  that reminds me, i'm gonna post the four agreements...  i want some feed back on them....  anyway, i'm not gonna get into everything matt and i said, but i just think it's funny when you can be sitting in a car with someone and tell them that you play mind games with them and know that they don't even realize your game...  it's not like either of us want to even play mind games anymore, but we're just kinda in the groove and it's hard to stop it....  or maybe we do wanna play them...  i don't know, it's too much to think about in the moring...

life amuses me greatly....  i love the way everything can get so fucked up by the smallest detail being off....  
nothing too major to report here...  just a feeling of uneasiness...  hopefully, it will leave me soon

so yesterday i decided that i need to honor what i say....   in bed, i say that you should try everything once....  well, i was not really sticking to that, but now i'm ready to....  anyway, i was looking at my horoscope today and it even told me that it's time....

Virgo...
Although your intuition is still working on overtime, it also may bring up unrealistic concerns over little things that, in the long run, won't matter. But how do you separate the real worries from the imagined? This is the dilemma. There's no quick and easy answer, but the solution is held by sensual Venus. Trust her. Move sensibly toward that which attracts you. 

...  oh yes, it's time...

have you ever known that something will never happen but still hoped for it?

i thought i had conditioned myself to not believe in certain things, but more and more i keep thinking about them....  what if?  what if?  what if i already know nothing will happen the way i want it to, but i still trick myself into thinking there's a chance?

i hate when i do this to myself...  it's torture....

so this guy comes into newshack yesterday when i was visiting steve....  he's a regular there and i know him pretty well...  anyway, his wife recently died and he needs help getting some of his housework done... i guess that's gonna be my new job....  Jill Marie, Housegirl... anyway, he's a cool guy and all....  really nice and he's a great connection in the business world in boca, so i know it'll be good to help him out (not in the sexual sense you nasty nasty people)

i try so hard...  i try to balance everything but i can't....  all i hear from every side of my life is "you're not doing enough" "u're not here enough"  "u obviously don't care if u can't make time for me"

i'm done....  peace out.... this game's over.... it's so hard when u love so many people and you want to build solid lasting bonds and yet are stuck with the problem that there's only 24 hours in a day and 6 of them have to be used for sleep!!!!!!!!!!!

i try so hard and i get no where!  i love so many and i all i get is feedback saying that it's not enough....  does that mean that i'm not enough?

i know some of u are reading this and thinking it's about you, but it's not.... it goes for everyone in my life, family, friends, coworkers.... over the past few weeks all i have been hearing is that i 'm not there enough or i'm not good enough..... well, i'm me, take me or leave me!

i know i sound all angry right now, but that's not it.... i'm actually at work trying to fight back the water from comin' out my eyes... if i could have one wish, just one it'd be that there were 40 hours in a day!  40 hours and i'd be able to get all my shit done and be able to see everyone i love everyday!  i hate not being able to be there for everyone....  i love you all and i wish i could BE more....

Virgo,
You have everything under control one minute and just a few moments later, it's all falling apart. People are just expecting too much of you now. Can't they just be satisfied with the special perspective that you bring to the situation? Things are coming at you from both sides and you are caught in a web of contradictions. Worry less about solutions and more about deflecting negativity.

how did this happen?  it's as if at one point in time i'm this smart kid...  everyone was breathing down my back, whispering in my ear "harvard or yale?  full scholarship for sure"...  then i discovered theater and it was "NYU here i come!"... i was bound and determined to be mimi marquez on RENT with brian as my roger!...  then years went by and it seems that i woke up one day and i'm trapped in the body of someone else.... man, what happened to me?  how did i get here?  i'm not gonna say that i hate my life, i fo' sho' don't...  i just don't get it.... i don't understand how i could have fucked up the track that far off course...

not just that, but how did i fuck up everything else?  how did i let my fear and need for comfort take over my life....  why do i value comfort so greatly?  why do i have problems letting go and putting my past behind me?  why can't i change my ways over night?

Thanksgiving is coming a bit early this year...  my parents seem to be leaving me alone this weekend...  thank God for that!!!!!!!!!!!!!!  i need time to relax and just chill with my friends...  no mom, no jeff...  i can't wait!!!!!!!!!

i think i try to kill everyhting that might be good for me...  i hide away from everything that might be a better change just so i can be safe and know what's gonna happen next.... why do i hate not knowing?

i need to make some changes, trust me i've been trying to change many of my habbits since the beginning of last summer, some i have been successful with, others i have not...  i think i need to really figure out what i want...  i mean, i think i know what it is, but it seems more and more my wants are fleeting...  it seems like i'll never be happy, no matter what dream i pursue or what i decide to do with my life...  maybe i should go away to a deserted island and just think...  prolly aftre a week (i'd need a week seeing as how u can't "just think" for a whole day and i'm sure i could find other stuff to do on the island) i'd know what i wanted....  then a few days later i'd completely change my mind....  i hate not being able to figure myself out...  it's so frustrating!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
i see the end of the world coming....  Bush may very well be the AntiChrist

so, i'm dumb...  this is what i should have said...
so, there's this guy at my work that i think might like me... he's a really great guy (sweet, fun, charming, silly, just plain amazing)...  and i am definitely liking him...  the problem, like always, is timing...  i wish i could just go full steam ahead into something with him, but i know i can't...  it wouldn't be fair...  it wouldn't be right to try to be with someone fully knowing you're not going to be able to be the best you can...  so i wanna wait...  i wanna wait until the timing's right...  i don't wanna blow my chances at having somehting real with him, just because i want him now...  that's not fair...  that's being selfish and also killing what could easily be one of the best things to happen to me...  i'm sorry

alright, so there's this guy at my work that i could tell from the start liked me...
anyway, we started hanging out (strictly friends) and we were having fun and then one night he kissed me...
 i thought i was developing feelings for him too and i thought that i might want something more with him...
he is head-over-heels for me while i just liked him (you know what i mean, not too strong feelings, but something)...
anyway, the last two times we started acting more "coupley" i guess and then last night he asked me what we were and i (a person that HATES being put on the spot) just kinda went with what he said not going out, but not together i guess...
so today i'm walking to class and it hits me, i think i might like the "idea" of being with him better than being with him...  i don't know i'm so confused...  i mean, it takes me a long time to develop feelings for someone and he's a really great guy and he'd be soooooooooo good to me and i like him, but i don't think i want anything serious, but i don't wanna hurt him and i don't wanna reject him b/c i could see myself liking him...
God, i am so over this confusion crap!

well, life is ever-changing and getting more interesting every day....  i'm not going inot detail just because i don't wanna jinx anything, but i'm sure u'll find out soon....  anyway, life's not so bad right now.... school sucks a fat one, but i'm sure most of you know how that is... this weekend's looking promising (my only real plan is to go down to see steve and blaze and whoever else, but i can't wait!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!)

last night was one of the craziest nights of my life...  it all started with jello shots and wine...  

then the stripper came.  he was hot.  i will try to scan a picture later and post it....  

then came the first bar where the bar tender took a liking to me.  he made my long island and then made me 2 shots to do with him...  

then we left that bar and i decided it was drunk dialing time... oh wait, did i mention we got an expedition limo to take us to the bars?...  anyway, then i drunk dialed steve and i knew i would never remember what the hell i told him...  i think i remember a miss you though but i MUST have been dreaming....

then more bars and more drinks and dancing with a real cute guy named chris...  then a garbage plate with jen at nick tahous...

then back to the hotel...  when we got there this girl named julie (must weigh like a good 350 easy)  yells out that she gave some guy head in the limo when we were at the bar...  the funniest part was that when we were in the limo this girl andrea said "eww, did i just put my hand in cum?" ...  we were all like, yeah right, it can't be... oh, it was...

alright, so i've done too much since the last time i updated.... here are a few highlights that i can remember....

this weekend was cool...  i hungout with people from my work and matt and 2/3 of TEAM DRIZZLE...  i saw my first triathalon...  damn, that shits cool...  i have a lot of training to do, but i see myself definitely doing one...  i also played mini-golf with mike, steve, and blaze...  i even didn't get last for once (sorry Blaze!!!!)...  other thank that, life's been good... 

...  i have finally decided that i am not looking to get married or have kids ever...  that doesn't mean that if i fall in love i just won't go for it, but i'm not looking for it...  it's a long story that will be brought up sometime when i'm not at my job...

...  as for the future, thursday morning at 430am  the car service comes to get mom, jeff, and i to go to rochester...  we're going for my cousin's wedding...  i come back monday and have a test monday night at 7...  my parents don't get back until thursday afternoon, so if u'd like to be penciled in to sleep next to me for a night, u know what number to call.... anyway, i gotta go  i'll post more about my thoughts later...

Your Boobies' Names Are: Cheech and Chong

Get your own Boobie Names

well, this hurricane's gonna fuck my schedule up again.... i thought finally i'd be able to hangout with some of my friends tonight, but noooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooo...  i can't....  this dumb hurricane watch means that my mom and jeff have to stay at work and i have to go home and clean and bring in the lawn furniture and stay at the house until the door guys are finished....  cinderella mop the floors....  cinderella do the laundry...  cinderella, cinderella, cinderella!!!!!!!!!!!  i'm so sick of not having a life right now...  i mean i know that my mom and jeff are having a hard time with shit, but why the fuck does it have to impact my life so fucking greatly....  just when we were finally getting back to normal...  just when i thought i'd be able to do what i want to do and not what i have to do....   man, i hate this shit!!!!!!

i fucked up my life....  my whole life....  i don't know what i'm doing or what i've done or what i want to do...  that's my real problem...  i don't know what i want
i hate being so indecisive...  it's fucking my whole life up...  maybe i'll take a year off from school...  i know if i do that though that it won't be any good...  i'll just waste my time like i do in the summer...  it'll be fun but it'll be a waste and i hate wasting time worse than anything...  i'm so confused

a sad little puppy sat in her window...
she looked out and dreamed of what could be...
if only she had a second chance to live life...
if only she could change her ways...
if only she could be loved...

how to rollover and play dead:
1) feel sick, so sick in fact that standingand talking is a chore
2) be bitchy and mean to any harmless person that crosses your path
3) turn your cell phone off so you can hide from the world
4) lay in bed and don't move all weekend, eventually someone will come by to see if 
   u are still breathing

I am also sorry to anyone who might have crossed my path this weekend, I'm sure I was a real big bitch...  Now, I am feeling better and I will try to make up anything I messed up last weekend...  I promise not to play dead again soon

so first i moved into the 19th century and got power...  now i have evolved into the 20th century...  here's how...

so matt took my car to do some tune-upish kinda work to it for my birthday...  i knew about it because i was there when he bought everything for it...yesterday he took it to work and did it all...  after he came to my house to swap cars back, we decided to take it out to see how it was driving now...  when i got in the car i saw it...  my evolution into the 20th century (yes i mean 20th, not 21st)... i finally have a cd player in my car!!!!!!!  he got one for my for my birthday!  how awesome is that????  i've never had one in a car of mine until now! 

in other news, the underwear war rages on at my house...  it all started when we didn't have power and jeff's mom took some of our clothes to wash for us...  anyway, she gave us back some clothes and my mom asked me if matt had an teal underwear...  i said no and she said "well this can't be jeff's"...  it's this pair of teal breifs that matt could fit into but jeff could never...  anyway, since i didn't take them, she decides to put them on my dresser...  i, inturn, put them on her outer doorknob...  she put them on my inner doorknob...  i throw them at her face when she walked by my room...  she threw them in my room as i closed my door to go to bed...  the next morning i hung them on her passenger side mirror...  i came home fromm the gym later that morning to find them on my ceiling fan and so i wrapped them on one of her shirts on a hanger in her closet...  by this time i thought she had gotten over it...  i go to climb into my bed taking off all my pillows and find them between my pillows...  i put them in her gym shoes this morning...  we'll see where the end up next, but if u got any good suggestions, leave them!

i would just like to tell everyone that i am no longer living in the dark as far as electricity goes...  I HAVE ELECTRICITY  finally....  it came on shortly after i hung up my sign outside that said "I'LL BLOW YOU FOR POWER!"... (just kidding but that's what i threatened my mom i would do if we didn't get power soon!)
